    {
        "id": 11,
        "user_id": null,
        "title": "프로그램 참가를 취소하면. 환불이 가능한가요?",
        "content": "<p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" id=\"SE-7dd5397a-5b17-41fa-9b39-908cd6fa25c6\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: unset; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" color:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" id=\"SE-44839c89-2c15-4540-afd1-504e41b31cbd\" malgun=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" style=\"line-height: inherit; box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit;\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; box-sizing: unset; font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">프로그램에 참여하기 위하여 대기하고 있는 학생들이 많습니다.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" id=\"SE-c3b482bf-8e9d-488f-9eba-0531f552cd29\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: unset; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" color:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" id=\"SE-30da28c0-4faf-431e-9619-f0266858127f\" malgun=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" style=\"line-height: inherit; box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit;\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; box-sizing: unset; font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">참여가 어려울 경우 빠른 취소 부탁드리며, 부득이하게 취소수수료가 발생하는 점 양해 바랍니다.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" id=\"SE-7f931e2d-0689-4861-93a9-2a3706a00c29\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: unset; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" color:=\"\" font-feature-settings:=\"\" font-kerning:=\"\" font-optical-sizing:=\"\" font-variation-settings:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" id=\"SE-3def9e39-18eb-4c85-9d74-71161e4c4d9f\" malgun=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\" style=\"line-height: inherit; box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit;\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; box-sizing: unset; font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">취소를 원하실 경우 전화 (02-880-4948\/02-888-0932~3) 혹은 이메일(nicemedu@snu.ac.kr) 로 연락주시기 바랍니다.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: unset; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); font-family: NotoSans, sans-serif; font-size: 16.1px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; width: 500px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 0px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; background-color: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">취소일<\/span><\/span><\/td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">취소수수료<\/span><\/span><\/td><\/tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">체험학습 참여 8일전까지<\/span><\/span><\/td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">없음<\/span><\/span><\/td><\/tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">체험학습 참여 7일전 ~ 3일전까지<\/span><\/span><\/td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">체험학습비의 50%<\/span><\/span><\/td><\/tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">체험학습 참여 2일전 ~ 당일<\/span><\/span><\/td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">체험학습비의 100%<\/span><\/span><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: unset; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;<\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); font-family: NotoSans, sans-serif; font-size: 16.1px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: initial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">( ※ 행정 처리 상의 문제로 환불 완료까지 최대 2주이상 소요될 수 있음을 양해바랍니다. ).<\/span><\/p>",
